  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, I don't have real-time access to Stanford University's current football season record. To find the most up-to-date information on Stanford Cardinal football's performance, including their win-loss record, scores, and standings, I recommend checking the following sources:\n\n1. **Stanford Athletics Official Website**: [gostanford.com](https://gostanford.com/sports/football)  \n   The official site provides comprehensive details about the team, including schedules, results, and news updates.\n\n2. **ESPN Stanford Football Page**: [ESPN Stanford Football](https://www.espn.com/college-football/team/_/id/225/stanford-cardinal)  \n   ESPN offers updated scores, statistics, and analysis for Stanford's football games.\n\n3. **NCAA Official Website**: [NCAA Football](https://www.ncaa.com/sports/football)  \n   The NCAA site provides standings, rankings, and other relevant information about college football teams, including Stanford.\n\n4. **Sports News Outlets**: Websites like [CBS Sports](https://www.cbssports.com/college-football/teams/Stanford/stanford-cardinal/), [Fox Sports](https://www.foxsports.com/college-football/stanford-cardinal-team), and [Yahoo Sports](https://sports.yahoo.com/stanford/) frequently update team records and game results.\n\nFor the most accurate and current record, please refer to one of these resources.",
